Class Salutation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vsfamily.vslib.common.VslibBaseClass
      • org.vsfamily.common.domain.Salutation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Salutation
extends VslibBaseClass
    Salutation class for implementing salutation codes. The sub-fields used in the database are:
    • id - system generated identifier [ long, not-null, primary key ] and
    • code - salutation code [ string , size(10), not-null, unique ].
